190  FLAGS = 0x001F,
191  ALL = 0x001F,
192  };

194

200  constexpr ValidFlags& operator|=(uint16_t val) { return *this = value | val; }
201  constexpr ValidFlags& operator&=(uint16_t val) { return *this = value & val; }

2744  constexpr bool disturbanceFlags() const { return (value & DISTURBANCE_FLAGS) > 0; }
2745  constexpr void disturbanceFlags(bool val) { value &= ~DISTURBANCE_FLAGS; if(val) value |= DISTURBANCE_FLAGS; }
2746  constexpr uint16_t flags() const { return (value & FLAGS) >> 0; }
2747  constexpr void flags(uint16_t val) { value = (value & ~FLAGS) | (val << 0); }
2748  constexpr bool allSet() const { return value == ALL; }
2749  constexpr void setAll() { value |= ALL; }
2750  };
2752  double time_of_week = 0;
2753  uint16_t week_number = 0;
2754  Vector3d alpha;
2755  uint8_t disturbance_flags = 0;
